# First install TiddlyWiki as described in [[Installing TiddlyWiki on Node.js]].
# Then edit the `tiddlywiki.info` file present in the new wiki folder:<br /><br />
## In the `plugins` section, add those lines:
#> `"tiddlywiki/tiddlyweb",
"tiddlywiki/filesystem",`
# Save the wiki then exit the process in the terminal and re-launch it in order for this take effect.<br /><br />
# To check if the modifications are functionnals:
#> Once you have re-launched your wiki, check for the presence of the plugins in the control panel, make sure they are not disabled.
#>And / or
#> Check for scrolling text in the opened terminal, under: <br />`Serving on 127.0.0.1:8080 (press ctrl-C to exit)`

